### Bug Description

[Y] I have updated to the latest stable version of n8n [2.29.10] and I am still experiencing this issue

I’m building an n8n workflow that appends one CSV row per form submission using Convert to File followed by Read/Write Files from Disk with append: true.

What I expected:
Each new execution should append a new record on the next line of the CSV file.

What actually happens:
New records are concatenated onto the previous line instead of starting on a new line.

Similar to previous issues raised in https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/issues/20834

### To Reproduce

[expense_tracker_bugs.csv](https://github.com/user-attachments/files/29956038/expense_tracker_bugs.csv)

